2. Create project

4. Define how to proceed.
For long files, it is better to go to “Translate a File”.
5 and 6. Define the languages to be translated into.

7. Once uploaded the automatic translation is done if this option was chosen.
8. From Tasks assign the people who are going to translate.

If the translator is not in Smartcat he/she will be invited by copying the project link.
